						<h4 class="product-title">HOW DOES THE FASHION FOR ALL WORK?</h4>
						<p class="product-description">The Fashion For All, as the name indicates, is a fashion website that enables customers to buy beautiful & unique clothing products sourced by us and created by independent designers. All our designers are vetted, before they can use our platform thus any product you buy, using our website, should be of the highest quality. </p>
