						<h4 class="product-title">HOW DO I MAKE A PURCHASE?</h4>
						<p class="product-description">Using The Fashion For All to buy products is very straight forward. You navigate around the site by clicking the store.  Once you have decided which product you want to buy, you click on the buy button. The product is then added to your shopping cart.</p>
						<hr>
						<h4 class="product-title">WHY SHOULD I BUY FROM THE FASHION FOR ALL?</h4>
						<p class="product-description">The Fashion For All selects the very best independent clothing designers to work with. This is to ensure our customers get the highest quality products and customer service. By purchasing from our website you get to own unique products which are in many cases made to order. So you are always going to be wearing something a little different from much of the mass produced fashion items out there.</p>
						<hr>
						<h4 class="product-title">AM I REQUIRED TO SET UP AN ACCOUNT BEFORE I PLACE AN ORDER?</h4>
						<p class="product-description">Registration is simple and will take you less than 60 seconds. Don't worry, we won't disclose your email address to any third parties, neither will we bombard your email account with irrelevant marketing promotions.p>
						<hr>
						<h4 class="product-title">CAN I CHANGE OR AMEND MY ORDER ONCE IT HAS BEEN PLACED?</h4>
						<p class="product-description">Before your purchases have been prepared for dispatch, by the designer, we can cancel an item. If you cancel an order after it has been dispatched you will have to return the order back to designer and a refund will be issued.</p>
						<hr>
						<h4 class="product-title">WHAT HAPPENS IF MY ORDER DOES NOT ARRIVE?</h4>
						<p class="product-description">If you haven't received your order within the time-frame indicated by the designer please contact us: info@thefashionforall.com. We will contact the designer on your behalf to determine an estimated delivery time.</p>
